Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.31,0:00:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.50,0:00:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.76,0:00:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.23,0:00:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.23,0:00:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.16,0:01:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The KC Grand Prix Opening Game"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.53,0:01:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Breakfast is ready~!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.25,0:01:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch~!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.30,0:01:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon and get up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.62,0:02:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! What the {\i1}hell{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.42,0:02:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You scared me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.59,0:02:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you expect? How long were you planning to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the problem? A lot's happened and we're {\i1}exhausted{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.59,0:02:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us sleep in peace~!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.15,0:02:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.49,0:02:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He ain't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where could he have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.83,0:02:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking at things now, it almost seems like everything that happened was just a bad dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.84,0:02:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't simply forget about that battle and everyone involved in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:02:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And about the Duel Monsters World...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:03:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And because of me, you've suffered greatly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, when we return to Japan, we can finally release the seal on your memory, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know exactly what will happen when we do...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter what happens, I won't forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...all the happy and painful moments I shared with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.13,0:03:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because they're memories that are precious to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.72,0:03:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is where you've been hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.39,0:03:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finished preparing breakfas...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DARLING!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez! You disappeared again and had me worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.36,0:03:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just taking a walk...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.53,0:03:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}E-Everyone's waiting... Let's go eat our breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.62,0:03:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.49,0:03:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're {\i1}so{\i0} slow, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.96,0:04:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.37,0:04:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and eat your food!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.92,0:04:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious~!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what are you all planning to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.34,0:04:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're planning to go back to Japan as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha? You don't have to rush! Take your time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! You're still on vacation, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you need advice, I'll be your tour guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great idea! We did come all the way to America, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.32,0:04:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Let's eat American cuisine! A {\i1}huge{\i0} steak and maybe some lobster!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.04,0:04:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is eating the only thing you care about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd ya say?! Then, Anzu, what're {\i1}you{\i0} gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.71,0:04:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.51,0:04:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.05,0:04:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me? Come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yugi... It'll be a big waste if we go back this soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.72,0:05:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... We have to hurry back and help the other Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as we have the God Cards back, there's no reason for us to rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.41,0:05:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isn't it okay for us to enjoy ourselves a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we've come all this way, let's enjoy ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.17,0:05:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.17,0:05:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! That's what I'm talkin' about!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you wanna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.05,0:05:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.89,0:05:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.72,0:05:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.60,0:05:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just went out somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.69,0:05:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looky, I think you guys should head to all the theme parks around the area!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Steaks! STEAKS!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta watch some American classics! Like, you know, those old western movies!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to have {\i1}steak{\i0} first!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:06:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long can you stay here? Have you figured out how you're going to get back yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me... How the heck {\i1}are{\i0} we getting home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! We came here at Pegasus' expense!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We never thought of how to get back home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much does a ticket cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.97,0:06:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... don't have any money!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.09,0:06:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me either...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, you can just live {\i1}here{\i0} for the rest of your life, Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! What about school?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.48,0:06:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba... Corporation?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.65,0:06:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what now? If that's all, I can get it done easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, Mokuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.74,0:06:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can send you back with one of Kaiba Corporation's private jets!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.12,0:06:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.83,0:06:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}However...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...under the condition that you enter
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the greatest Duel Monsters Tournament ever held by Kaiba Corporation, the KC Grand Prix!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what's the deal with this Duel tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know Kaiba Land's going to open in America, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I saw it in the news. They said it was almost completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.35,0:07:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And for it's grand opening, we're holding a huge Duel tournament in place of an opening ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm very sorry, Seto-{\i0}sama{\i1}...\NWe're doing our very best, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sick and tired of hearing this over and over!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Start showing me some {\i0}results{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Y-Yes sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You did get back all the stocks Doma bought, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But after this incident, Kaiba Corporation was left with enormous debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.22,0:07:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The stock price is very low.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}God, this is really annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But once our tournament starts up,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}everyone is sure to be turning their attention to Kaiba Corporation again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If it works, all of those bad rumors will be tarnished!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.48,0:08:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isono, how's the registration on our network going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes, it is underway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Also, are you still planning to invite those guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of {\i0}course{\i1} we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They owe us for a lot of aid we gave them before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In that case, let me get to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isono, I'm going too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mokuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Leave it to me, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll be sure to get those guys to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why I've come to pick you guys up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, man! Aren't you guys just deciding that on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this situation, shouldn't Kaiba come here bowing his head and begging us to join?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba Corporation's all about propaganda, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if Battle City Finalists like Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0} and Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} take part,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll be all over the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.95,0:08:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm {\i1}telling{\i0} you...! My brother's really busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he's the organizer of this tournament, he's too busy to even {\i1}join{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba's{\i0} not gonna {\i1}Duel{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must really be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now{\i0} I get it. He's afraid of losin' to me and Yugi, so he's not even gonna show his face, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.35,0:09:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's beaten again, Kaiba Corporation's reputation will fall through the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell my brother would lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that... His job as a CEO is far more important than being a Duelist at the moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All to fulfill our dream of spreading Kaiba Land throughout the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.16,0:09:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi, you went too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he really does have it hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, this tournament is putting the future of Kaiba Corporation on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're aiming to hold the greatest Duels with the strongest Duelists chosen from around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm asking you to join. As the Duel King!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duelists from around the world? Sounds exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we'll have fun Dueling there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.53,0:10:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you'll enter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.21,0:10:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Yugi's gonna do it, count me in too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll enter too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.91,0:10:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the U.S. Champion, I should be entitled to!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.29,0:10:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say Darling, let's go sign up together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.71,0:10:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! I planned on asking you as well, so I brought your invitation with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.26,0:10:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me the greatest Duels!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave it to us. Right, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now this event will surely be amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:11:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Herr{\i0} Sieg, you have received a new e-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.39,0:11:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"KC Grand Prix," eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How inexperienced you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You believe holding this event will restore the faith consumers once had in Kaiba Corporation, Seto Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bet your life on this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:12:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kaiba Land USA!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}so{\i0} big!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.76,0:12:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sure got a lot of attractions!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to attractions and size, there's nothing like this in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like fun! Right, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.69,0:12:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go on a date after the opening, Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the hell? I wanna stay with Yugi too...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.66,0:12:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Money sure does talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the main gate, where the shopping carts are located.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of {\i1}course{\i0} it's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.17,0:12:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, Jounouchi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.14,0:12:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Mokuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.43,0:12:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.81,0:12:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you invited many outstanding Duelists to this tournament, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:12:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! The best in the {\i1}world{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.25,0:13:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well in that case, Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you also invite Mai Kujaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I did include her in the invitation list...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.93,0:13:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we have no idea of her whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.62,0:13:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing her, she's probably off somewhere nice and healthy and Dueling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? There's some people here already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Admission's free for today because it's the opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.93,0:13:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys can play around all you want later as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.14,0:13:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,AWRIGHT!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna ride the rollercoasters!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.65,0:13:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YEAH!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're both so childish...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.61,0:13:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this'll be the Duel Stadium for the tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes Dome...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't normal people call this "going too far"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:13:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Main Duel Stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.37,0:14:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The entire Duel will be broadcast around the whole world!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The {\i1}whole{\i0} world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.25,0:14:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to be careful not to embarrass yourself out there Dueling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I attack Blade Knight with Gagagigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.27,0:14:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Quick-Play Magic activate, Scapegoat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Why are you using Scapegoat {\i1}now{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just ended my turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this computer? Doesn't it know how to Duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be planning to use that reverse card over there, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.58,0:14:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.46,0:14:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Activating Trap Card. DNA Surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.79,0:14:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as this card remains on the field...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.25,0:14:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}every Monster on the field will become a Type I choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.68,0:14:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will choose the Dragon-Type.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Gagagigo...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.06,0:15:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Furthermore, activating Magic Card from hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fusing all its Monsters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.69,0:15:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will fuse together all Dragon-Type Monsters on field...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...Summoning Five God Dragon onto field.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.33,0:15:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you {\i1}kidding{\i0} me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Five-God Dragon with {\i1}5000{\i0} Attack Points?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.84,0:15:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's a computer, it has such advanced tactics...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surprised, are we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Duel Computer is installed with elite Duelist card data from across the globe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that of course includes my brother, Yugi and even {\i1}Jounouchi's{\i0} data.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.60,0:15:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi's data{\i0}? So it depends on luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.77,0:15:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say that again!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.57,0:15:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't it pointless to fight against such a powerful computer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.86,0:15:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:16:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a level setter so even beginners can enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is one of Kaiba Land's specialties!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.37,0:16:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's interesting! You can even Duel against yourself with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.67,0:16:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five-God Dragon, attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.06,0:16:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we told you the level was set too high.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go next!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.37,0:16:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you learned something good from that. Now you can re-construct your deck for next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,AHH! It's the Duel King, Yugi Mutou!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.57,0:16:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.49,0:16:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! It really is him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.28,0:16:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And even the American Champion, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.47,0:16:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please gimme your autograph!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing! Yugi's become famous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.41,0:16:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Leon. I've admired your Duels for a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm moved to be able to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.34,0:16:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Hey! Want my autograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:16:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:16:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who {\i1}are{\i0} you, dude?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}See? It's Katsuya Jounouchi from the Battle City Best Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.48,0:17:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never heard of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.17,0:17:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.31,0:17:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... Would you mind looking at my deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.32,0:17:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.57,0:17:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always lose... How can I be as strong as you, Yugi-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.12,0:17:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? They're all Dragon-Types.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.66,0:17:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like Dragons, so I traded with my friends and got a whole bunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.67,0:17:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that you like them, but the balance here is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright. Liking your cards will only make them stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your cards will respond to your thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.31,0:17:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.03,0:17:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.53,0:17:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's not a Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that card is sure to help your Dragons out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.33,0:18:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want one too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Yugi, what card was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.17,0:18:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.96,0:18:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try this out in a Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.22,0:18:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better not set the level too high!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll challenge Level Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A greeting is in order. A friendly {\i1}grüßen{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-{\i1}Duel.{\i0}\N -Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What? A blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.00,0:18:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, it's dangerous, so don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, Mokuba! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange... This shouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it needs a tune-up. There could be some kind of problem with the system.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway... Stay calm, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.64,0:19:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power'll be back soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did the emergency shutters go off?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use, it won't work! This is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.29,0:19:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The program has been locked and the entire system has been connected to the Duel Computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.13,0:19:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't stop the Duel Computer, we can't open the exits.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could this even happen? This computer was designed for Dueling only!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.43,0:19:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with the main system!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone hacked the system from the outside and rewrote the programming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:20:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But who could've done something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.65,0:20:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't figure that much out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... We just have to destroy the computer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.57,0:20:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.16,0:20:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, we'll never get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what {\i1}should{\i0} we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.71,0:20:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Duel Computer is beaten, the locks should open.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.84,0:20:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the only way out is to defeat it in a Duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.80,0:20:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.47,0:20:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Duel start. My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.47,0:20:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Summoning Berserk Gorilla in Attack Position.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.64,0:20:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I also set one reverse card card and end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Dueling him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.27,0:20:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the level?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.53,0:20:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the highest level?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a child fighting against it! Can he win?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.32,0:20:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared~!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.83,0:20:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't fight in this position.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.43,0:20:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The deck's been chosen already. We can't change it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.29,0:20:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.33,0:20:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to play with that horribly unbalanced Dragon Deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that'll beat the computer at its highest level!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.76,0:21:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.48,0:21:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.42,0:21:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.14,0:21:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.44,0:21:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your name is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rick... You put all your feelings into that deck. Please let me borrow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.36,0:21:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.86,0:21:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.12,0:21:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darling! You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.70,0:21:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.33,0:21:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be your opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get everyone out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.27,0:22:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.63,0:22:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.24,0:22:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.31,0:22:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.79,0:22:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.07,0:22:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.97,0:22:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.12,0:23:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.64,0:23:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.16,0:23:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't the KC Grand Prix sound pretty fun?
